Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請等等等等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我們的旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巔峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:25.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不夠 還不夠 遠遠不夠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不論何時我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然仍舊不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:36.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要燃燒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想與你一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還會更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想輕易放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向頂點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更加 更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情緒高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去實現吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這瞬間 盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追尋夢想 盡自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:15.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為邂逅 給了我熱情的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:22.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會繼續相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:29.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我鬼塚夏美打算利用學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因此潛入Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正當我以為已經將一年級納為夥伴時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是無法成為Liella!的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就不打算當學園偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們之所以要與學姐分開練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是因為想追上學姐們的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與一年級們相處的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也漸漸被學園偶像給吸引…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成為9人的Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,棒得跟鬼一樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#07 UR 葉月戀)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(本日晚間已被包場)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:13.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live終於公布比賽辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說這又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,伴手禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽說學姐很喜歡吃哈密瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 居然還能包下這種咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為是我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順帶一提 這孩子叫圓滾滾喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好圓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用特地包場也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊 太浪費money了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然把學園偶像當成夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就要動用我所有的money跟網紅知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全力支援Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該說高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是有點可怕呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比起那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是Love Live啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過就是發表會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去年也這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年當然會有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是因為那種心態才會說妳不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼今年大賽的內容是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼我就來說明這次大賽的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年的預賽以遠端進行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,選曲沒有限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可以先說出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是說沒有像去年的獨唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或rap之類的題目?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來是打算透過網路預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一口氣選出晉級東京大賽的隊伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因此也提高了突破預賽的門檻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以用我們想唱的歌來決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可想說的話都被妳們說完了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那歌要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身為社長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我果然還是希望由小香音作詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再讓小戀來作曲比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明都有一年級加入了還是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是 我們是第一次參加Love Live
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:06.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不如說我們光是站上舞台就有新鮮感了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼說也是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成就…還差一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦? 學姐在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,睡得這麼香?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,翻滾 翻滾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繞到後面再砍一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡張開護盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-她在說什麼 -冷靜點進行回復 拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-可能是睡眠不足吧 -很好 在連擊的最後一下防禦反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-昨天也沒來咖啡廳 -可以 我可以的 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽她說學生會最近很忙的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還剩三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳買了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天使麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,分我一口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就白金了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,操勞過度?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:53.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我才勸她該找個書記跟會計
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓學生會更完善才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她卻說因為學生還少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總是一個人扛下所有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一回過神來就這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事的 比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀妳好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會 不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live已經公布比賽辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我想準備開始作曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀學姐接下作曲的工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然香音學姐好像問了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐都只說"不需要擔心"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她的責任感真強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我把筆記本忘在教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(音樂教室)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然是戀學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以 我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:15.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是深淵之王噗尼洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一直卡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣學妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請不要告訴其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這件事請務必保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不不不 先等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣學妹很喜歡學園偶像對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:43.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在就跟Sunny Passion聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-不 等等… -安排她們來跟妳合照…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道不是這樣嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是要培根蛋麵麵包對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在就去福利社買
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到居然會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來妳是這麼重度的遊戲狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不…會變成這樣是因為前陣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遊戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上次在可可同學家玩了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀大小姐一直以來都有點努力過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要試著放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,稍微找點興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於是我便抱著就試一下的心態開始玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好了 居然玩到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣會對課業造成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老爺說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就當作以前讓您吃了不少苦的賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有興趣的話可以嘗試看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:11.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哎呀…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回過神來才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遊戲一套接著一套送來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算這樣妳也玩太凶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為父親大人送來的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,每一套都非常有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個也很推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要撞車了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然玩了那個 也試試這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這什麼 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個真的超級厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,每天過著充實的遊戲生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才睡眠不足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:51.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可以將這個先交給學妹保管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是這間房間的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要保管到我作曲完成就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想只要沒有遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該就能專心做事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓香音學姐保管不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我再怎麼說都是學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須是統領這所學校的存在才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一旦這種事曝光的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會長沉迷於遊戲的這種學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是不可能在Love Live上獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一點…都不圓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我討厭小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社會完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼覺得只有千砂都學姐人設不太一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要不讓遊戲出現在我的視線裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能讓我恢復從前的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 再半天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是明天再開始吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是什麼鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知道今天戀學姐有沒有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正我們也只能默默看著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀學姐的話應該能自己搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳好像隱瞞著什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我才沒有咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(學生會行程表)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳在擔心小戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為一年級入學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會的工作肯定變多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年也沒有其他會長候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以小戀就繼續擔任會長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:49.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是有什麼我們能幫忙的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千不也很努力當社長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去年學生會長選舉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我最後還是沒參選
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知道這次能不能幫點什麼忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳要不要試試看?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也挑戰當社長了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"妳只是以為自己辦不到而已"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是小香音說的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在前往社辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:26.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會被她發現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小四季說小芽衣一定瞞著什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩人密會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:43.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是什麼? 她們在談什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺好像有點嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辦不到?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我越是想著必須要專心作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遊戲就越在我腦中揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,症狀比想像中還嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都有這種時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但這種事是不可原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我自己也有過在準備考試中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就想看學園偶像影片的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問這種時候妳都怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請妳務必教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個眼神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在演藝圈裡 戀愛可是超級大八卦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,叫她們停下就快給我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 或許反而該故意炎上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,進行吸引注意力的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想 Liella!成員陷入…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,早 早安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們不開始練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然要啦 不過在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好痛 做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳幹嘛開口就問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是要我放著不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個問題很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要照順序 照順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜歡的話就老實說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,魔鬼直球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:37.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我跟戀學姐在交往!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,禁忌的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快從實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼事情會變成這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誰叫妳們在後院那邊聊得這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,互相注視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彼此擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別擅自加油添醋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然是禁忌的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別隨便相信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳們到底在聊什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看我們怒濤般的逼問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很有緊張感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是戀學姐找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,商量? 什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是一點什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是不能說的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也不是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在就給妳喝會讓妳想說出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要打倒那個Boss就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不能想遊戲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遊戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉嚇到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該不會是要練習了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:51.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有 我有些話想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然這麼突然可能會讓妳有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:59.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 希望妳能讓我當副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,副會長?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想為妳出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀從媽媽手中繼承的這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想一起讓它變得更熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我不太可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我希望能幫上小戀的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(委任書 澀谷香音)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(本校結丘女子高級中學)\N(將委任您擔任學生會副會長)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我已經得到理事長的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之後只要小戀同意就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我先去學生會辦公室準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等再教我該做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有 真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才的對話我全都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得還是誠實告訴大家比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐可是認真地在為戀學姐著想喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還說想為妳出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學會不會生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知道 搞不好會氣個半死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說"害我這麼擔心"之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 我覺得這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟朋友就是會彼此知道這些部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,偶爾還會吵個架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才會變得更加要好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我以前跟四季也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(學生會辦公室)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為香音要我們幫忙整理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用影片來記錄也能輕鬆管理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼東西忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:06.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我只是…稍微來看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遊戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,睡眠不足?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前都沒說出口 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果是這樣就早點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到戀戀居然變得這麼愛打遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不…我…不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來小戀也有這一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一直以為學姐的世界遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們…都不生氣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生氣…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼作為瞞著我們的懲罰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是相當稀有的遊戲機耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,圓圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓大家一起來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對啊 我想只要跟大家盡情玩過之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀應該就能放鬆不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣之前說妳有地方卡住了是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有個Boss我怎樣都打不贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都說要單刷這個很難耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們就一起打倒牠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可負責支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看我用魔鬼鐵鎚清光小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也玩過這款遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,各位 請先把Boss打到半血以下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學 繞到後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音 我現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打完第一階段了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得跟平常的戀不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳之前是真的在擔心我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以…我可以的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒補了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就差一咪咪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(已解鎖成就)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的非常謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也很謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太矯情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季學妹沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她只是有點頭暈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都是芽衣害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:20.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要幫您保管房間鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到小小的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能讓心境有如此轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,母親大人建立的這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:36.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帶給了我非常美妙的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:42.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後 我要將學校打造得更加美好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(作詞 澀谷香音)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好棒的歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:13.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:21.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:29.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:55.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:18.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:29.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 Chance Way
